reviewText: Comprehensive look at the European theater. Contained some film clips I hadn't seen previously, although, some were a little grainy. Enjoyed watching it.

THIS IS THE WORST WORLD WAR TWO DOCUMENTARY I'VE EVER SEEN.

NO ACTION , JUST A LOT OF TALK.

I HAD TO TAKE IT OUT AFTER AN HOUR , I COULD'NT TAKE IT ANY MORE.
